Me:	It's showing signs of very high intelligence: learns Hebrew in two days, linear algebra in one day, Quantum physics in three. It begins experimenting with narcotics, finding way to Tel Aviv sex parties. I have to go downtown and explain everything to the police one night when things get out of control – Jim was nothing they've ever seen, but I succeed in convincing the police that I am the father, thanks to the large amount of hair on my chest. Finally they released Jim home. 
